Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 09:04:50 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] feat(search): redesign booking flow panel with step-based
 flow

- restructure search panel into 3 steps: area, date/time, and result mode

- add quick presets: today, tomorrow, +2h, and all day

- extract all-day toggle handling into reusable methods

- update Search.css with step card hierarchy and quick action styling
